    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When a routine job gets knocked suddenly off course, young astronaut <strong>Riley</strong> is left stranded deep in space and needs to find her way back home to a world she's struggling to find her place in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With three of the <strong>warp relays</strong> - which allow humanity to travel light-years in the blink of an eye - taken offline,<strong> </strong>her only option is to master control of her little ship and complete the challenging trials needed to reboot the relays.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009130/extras/5f232f7d4903c66b1adb743265f90bcb.poster.avif?t=1770673916\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009130/extras/5f232f7d4903c66b1adb743265f90bcb.webm?t=1770673916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009130/extras/5f232f7d4903c66b1adb743265f90bcb.mp4?t=1770673916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rocket through more than 20 tightly-crafted top-down levels, mastering your ship's momentum-based movement to evade hazards, complete objectives, and restore power to the relays.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your ship and restore its lost abilities, allowing you to overcome new obstacles.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race the clock and try to beat each level's target time by perfecting your route and pushing your speed to the limit.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover secret items hidden inside every level, giving extra glimpses into Riley's life back home and rewarding you with new paint jobs for your ship.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009130/extras/c75861b971bcfbbda600702ef5507683.poster.avif?t=1770673916\" width=1170 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009130/extras/c75861b971bcfbbda600702ef5507683.webm?t=1770673916\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009130/extras/c75861b971bcfbbda600702ef5507683.mp4?t=1770673916\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
